{"tid":899641,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇過《孤高之人》同一作者新作《純真之人》？","createTime":"2018-11-12T15:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T16:41:13.000Z","uid":82558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"247da7e6f5c006152ac69f1f46a06dab783d67a8","tid":899641,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:17:02.000Z","msg":"知道好多人都睇過神作《孤高之人》，可能取材同前作好唔同，同作者既《純真之人》就比較少人睇，但其實都係非常高水準既漫畫，啲大場面好似文藝復興時期啲畫咁好好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n故事內容就係講法國劊子手桑松家族同法國歷史既淵源，所以有血腥處刑同裸露畫面，同埋係學到嘢既（最近睇到發明斷頭檯嗰part知道點先可以完整切嗰頭落嚟）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-kbcla7KhiUQ/V1N1qzVDyOI/AAAAAAAAH94/tc9l5ezeXlE0VNVlXgaGaADCtFHBRrP0wCCo/s0/7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-kbcla7KhiUQ%2FV1N1qzVDyOI%2FAAAAAAAAH94%2Ftc9l5ezeXlE0VNVlXgaGaADCtFHBRrP0wCCo%2Fs0%2F7.jpg&h=fe0ede08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://mikachina-bbs.b0.upaiyun.com/wp/2017/12/innocent7_fixw_640_hq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmikachina-bbs.b0.upaiyun.com%2Fwp%2F2017%2F12%2Finnocent7_fixw_640_hq.jpg&h=fa26be5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i3.mangareader.net/innocent-rouge/1/innocent-rouge-8173951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi3.mangareader.net%2Finnocent-rouge%2F1%2Finnocent-rouge-8173951.jpg&h=e4ea8142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/736x/30/22/31/302231332f3bafcf0728ed30f20df13b--innocent-manga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F736x%2F30%2F22%2F31%2F302231332f3bafcf0728ed30f20df13b--innocent-manga.jpg&h=1dfd30bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/16a6053c6b243fefcff5c1b6c7d86ba1/tumblr_ohfmbgMj5u1ri9hnio2_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F16a6053c6b243fefcff5c1b6c7d86ba1%2Ftumblr_ohfmbgMj5u1ri9hnio2_1280.png&h=e726172d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲畫風靚到呢（根本完全冇動畫化既可能）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文版斷更之後一直睇英文版，睇到rouge最新單行本<br />\n中文版，但斷更，有啲畫面有刪減<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英文版就齊既，其實西方歷史睇英文版會更好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人睇過可以討論下？"},{"pid":"b7fdd4d15714cad3d792d8726afd22c7e21e8dd3","tid":899641,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cee9e0eee0654dec57118b1f76d72ad304b935e","tid":899641,"uid":9183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"瑪麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐冇漢化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6567d0eb1bf532fc31cc53951e7daa9c4ac698","tid":899641,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cee9e0eee0654dec57118b1f76d72ad304b935e","tid":899641,"uid":9183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"瑪麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐冇漢化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3773428daf8c720440ac7de0466b9836383ebefe","tid":899641,"uid":9183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf6567d0eb1bf532fc31cc53951e7daa9c4ac698","tid":899641,"uid":82558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cee9e0eee0654dec57118b1f76d72ad304b935e","tid":899641,"uid":9183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"瑪麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐冇漢化<img src=\"/assets